item.title: CVE-2020-15110|2024-08-04T13:08:22.300Z -- jupyterhub -- kubespawner
item.description: In jupyterhub-kubespawner before 0.12, certain usernames will be able to craft particular server names which will grant them access to the default server of other users who have matching usernames. This has been fixed in 0.12.
